  "privacyDataStorageBody": "All data is stored exclusively on your device:\n\n• SSH credentials are stored in the device's secure storage (iOS Keychain / Android EncryptedSharedPreferences).\n• Connection configurations are stored in a local SQLite database within the app's private sandbox.\n• No data is transmitted to external servers or third parties.\n• No analytics, telemetry, or crash data is collected.",
